emulib.plugins.cpu

Class DisassembledInstruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • emulib.plugins.cpu.DisassembledInstruction

  • public class DisassembledInstruction
extends Object
    This class represents disassembled instruction. It is used by disassembler. It is implemented as read/write container that stores address, mnemo and opcode of the instruction.
